<del rend="strikethrough"> ge </del><expan>mache<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> het </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_218_line_1576593440810_5605">vvolt </ab></add> / biſʒ der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> hinab </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r2l30"><expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> moht </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_218_line_1586607936427_576">
<del rend="strikethrough">ſein </del> mag </ab></add> / vnd tüt darynne durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vville<ex>n</ex></expan> Als vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r2l31">euch des wol <expan>getr<ex>awen</ex></expan> / das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc / <expan>Act<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r2l32"><expan>Purifıc<ex>acionis</ex></expan> . <expan>M<ex>arie</ex></expan> . Anno <expan>vndecı<ex>m</ex>o</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_218" id="108v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Heincze<ex>n</ex></expan> Gertner,
                            <expan>schulth<ex>eisz</ex></expan>, und den gesworen czu Eyffelstat
                    </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan> freuntschaft bevor.
                                                  <expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> freunde, uns hat
                                                  <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Hans
                                                Lengenfelder <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, wie im Cuncz Örter
                                                und Andres, sein pruder, <add>gesessen</add> bey ew
                                                czu Eyfelstat, sein weine verpoten
                                                  <expan>hete<ex>n</ex></expan>, die sie in füren
                                                und <add>im die</add> ledig
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lassen, also daz er
                                                in <expan>v<ex>er</ex>pürgen</expan> müst, daz er
                                                hinab <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> und in des
                                                rehten <add><expan>danyde<ex>n</ex></expan> sein
                                                  wolt</add>. Nu spricht der
                                                  <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, daz er selber
                                                  <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> czu ew
                                                  <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> und in des
                                                  <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan> gewesen <add>sein
                                                  wolt</add>, <add>so</add> ist ez
                                                  <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> als
                                                  <expan>unfridlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> im lande, daz
                                                er vor unfride hinab niht tar, als ir das selber
                                                auch wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sten</expan> mügt.
                                                  <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> so
                                                  <expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan> wir euch
                                                  <expan>freuntlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz ir die
                                                  <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Örter daran
                                                weysen wöllet, daz sie dem
                                                  <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> sein
                                                  <expan>pürge<ex>n</ex></expan> ledig sagen; und
                                                  <expan>hete<ex>n</ex></expan> sie
                                                  <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> czu dem
                                                  <expan>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> icht
                                                  <expan>czespr<ex>echen</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir in
                                                  <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ire<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheinbot<ex>en</ex></expan> etc. ut in
                                                  <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>. Möht aber des niht
                                                gesein, daz ir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> ein
                                                  <expan>lenge<ex>r</ex></expan> frist
                                          <add><expan>hieczwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <app><note><q type="date">sant
                                            <expan>Walp<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>en</ex></expan> tag</q>01.05.1411</note></app>
                                            oder auf <app><note><q type="date"><expan>ost<ex>er</ex>n</expan></q>12.04.1411</note></app></add>
                                                darynne <expan>beredt</expan> und
                                                  <expan>mache<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>wolt</add>, bisz der
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> hinab
                                                  <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>mag</add>; und tüt darynne durch
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>, als wir euch des wol
                                                  <expan>getr<ex>awen</ex></expan>. Das
                                                  <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                                                  <expan>Act<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>purific<ex>acionis</ex></expan>
<expan>M<ex>arie</ex></expan>, anno
                                                  <expan>undeci<ex>m</ex>o</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
